{"tid":258563,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"41歲男子考車牌 向運輸署考牌主任行賄$5000","createTime":"2017-05-26T08:37:48.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-26T17:22:27.000Z","uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"cdd203fd3839334a8ae2df0729bd90ef9c008901","tid":258563,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T08:37:48.000Z","msg":"一名男子被指涉嫌在考車牌期間，向運輸署考牌主任行賄，被廉政公署今日（5月26日）落案起訴，控以一項向公職人員提供利益罪名。男子暫准保釋，5月31日在觀塘裁判法院應訊。<br />\n<br />\n控罪指，一名41歲男子4月5日 到運輸署轄下的駕駛考試中心參加私家車路試，涉嫌向運輸署一名二級考牌主任提供利益，即一封5000港元的利是，作為將其私家車駕駛考試的駕駛技巧及表現評為及格的報酬。<br />\n<br />\n廉政公署早前接獲運輸署轉介的貪污投訴，展開調查。今日落案起訴他一項向公職人員提供利益罪名。"},{"pid":"646d31cd4742f3d6e0721c62ad37b6aa07bb27b2","tid":258563,"uid":73722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T08:40:00.000Z","msg":"屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />實係支那畜落黎以為呢度用支那個套行得通"},{"pid":"a9904d9340c824e26d1a5bda8232ca9b801d3272","tid":258563,"uid":29879,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T08:44:07.000Z","msg":"5000蚊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55c930bdb432652ebab8c5ab7611ea19e0fd9378","tid":258563,"uid":70786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T08:45:09.000Z","msg":"垃圾廢老"},{"pid":"bebe46276f5f36515a8f5edafcb8f706408aacea","tid":258563,"uid":60655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T08:46:46.000Z","msg":"考牌 icac捉得好嚴"},{"pid":"26fdb3217d3a4d9d14d3ee7940e20b192b5ae5b6","tid":258563,"uid":52946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T08:48:40.000Z","msg":"5萬個阿sir可能會考慮下既"},{"pid":"e36d0c9055eb5e51436ba9db03373407eeccc832","tid":258563,"uid":27240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T08:54:29.000Z","msg